d forty nights, and I will wipe from the face of the earth every living thing I have made.”"}, {:version=>"New American Standard Bible ", :text=>"\"For after seven more days, I will send rain on the earth forty days and forty nights; and I will blot out from the face of the land every living thing that I have made.\""}, {:version=>"New King James Version", :text=>"For after seven more days I will cause it to rain on the earth forty days and forty nights, and I will destroy from the face of the earth all living things that I have made.”"}, {:version=>"King James Bible", :text=>"For yet seven days, and I will cause it to rain upon the earth forty days and forty nights; and every living substance that I have made will I destroy from off the face of the earth."}, {:version=>"Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"Seven days from now I will make it rain on the earth forty days and forty nights, and every living thing I have made I will wipe off the face of the earth.\""}, {:version=>"Contemporary English Version", :text=>"Seven days from now I will send rain that will last for 40 days and nights, and I will destroy all other living creatures I have made. "}, {:version=>"Good News Translation", :text=>"Seven days from now I am going to send rain that will fall for forty days and nights, in order to destroy all the living beings that I have made.\" "}, {:version=>"Holman Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"Seven days from now I will make it rain on the earth 40 days and 40 nights, and I will wipe off from the face of the earth every living thing I have made.\" "}, {:version=>"International Standard Version", :text=>"Seven days from now I'll send rain on the earth for 40 days and 40 nights, and I'll destroy every living creature that I've made.\""}, {:version=>"NET Bible", :text=>"For in seven days I will cause it to rain on the earth for forty days and forty nights, and I will wipe from the face of the ground every living thing that I have made.\" "}, {:version=>"New Heart English Bible", :text=>"In seven days, I will cause it to rain on the earth for forty days and forty nights. Every living thing that I have made, I will destroy from the surface of the ground.\""}, {:version=>"GOD'S WORD® Translation", :text=>"In seven days I will send rain to the earth for 40 days and 40 nights. I will wipe off the face of the earth every living creature that I have made.\""}, {:version=>"JPS Tanakh 1917", :text=>"For yet seven days, and I will cause it to rain upon the earth forty days and forty nights; and every living substance that I have made will I blot out from off the face of the earth.'"}, {:version=>"New American Standard 1977 ", :text=>"“For after seven more days, I will send rain on the earth forty days and forty nights; and I will blot out from the face of the land every living thing that I have made.”"}, {:version=>"King James 2000 Bible", :text=>"For yet seven days, and I will cause it to rain upon the earth forty days and forty nights; and every living thing that I have made will I destroy from off the face of the earth."}, {:version=>"American King James Version", :text=>"For yet seven days, and I will cause it to rain on the earth forty days and forty nights; and every living substance that I have made will I destroy from off the face of the earth."}, {:version=>"American Standard Version", :text=>"For yet seven days, and I will cause it to rain upon the earth forty days and forty nights; and every living thing that I have made will I destroy from off the face of the ground."}, {:version=>"Brenton Septuagint Translation", :text=>"For yet seven days "}, {:version=>" I bring rain upon the earth forty days and forty nights, and I will blot out every offspring which I have made from the face of all the earth.", :text=>"Douay-Rheims Bible"}, {:version=>"For yet a while, and after seven days, I will rain upon the earth forty days and forty nights; and I will destroy every substance that I have made, from the face of the earth. ", :text=>"Darby Bible Translation"}, {:version=>"For in yet seven days I will cause it to rain on the earth forty days and forty nights; and every living being which I have made will I destroy from the ground.", :text=>"English Revised Version"}, {:version=>"For yet seven days, and I will cause it to rain upon the earth forty days and forty nights; and every living thing that I have made will I destroy from off the face of the ground.", :text=>"Webster's Bible Translation"}, {:version=>"For yet seven days, and I will cause it to rain upon the earth forty days and forty nights: and every living substance that I have made will I destroy from the face of the earth.", :text=>"World English Bible"}, {:version=>"In seven days, I will cause it to rain on the earth for forty days and forty nights. Every living thing that I have made, I will destroy from the surface of the ground.\"", :text=>"Young's Literal Translation"}, {:version=>" for after other seven days I am sending rain on the earth forty days and forty nights, and have wiped away all the substance that I have made from off the face of the ground.'", :text=>nil}]}